"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/516870","Ministry of Justice","false","2016-05-05","<p>This information is published and available within the Ministry of Justice Official Tribunal Statistics and can be found at: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/tribunals-statistics" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/tribunals-statistics</a>.</p>","North West Cambridgeshire","Mr Shailesh Vara",,"2016-05-05T09:45:33.98Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/516870/answer","Biography information for Mr Shailesh Vara","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/516870/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/516870/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2016-04-29","Employment Tribunals Service: Fees and Charges","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many people have had employment tribunal fees waived or reduced in each year since the introduction of such fees.","false","Biography information for Andy Slaughter","Hammersmith","Andy Slaughter","36163"
